        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Conical vs flat burr for pour-over: which gives better clarity?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Flat burr grinders often produce higher clarity and separation, while conical burr grinders usually offer more body and forgiving sweetness. Choose based on cup style preference and workflow."}
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Manual or electric grinder: which is better for daily pour-over use?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Manual grinders are excellent for value and one-cup routines. Electric grinders are usually better for speed, convenience, and repeated daily brews."}
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How do I reduce fines, bitterness, or sludge in pour-over cups?",
